name: LRUMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of LRUMap, focusing on the behavior of retrieving keys with and without updating to the Most Recently Used (MRU) position.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKeyWithUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an existing key and ensures it updates to the MRU position.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKeyWithoutUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an existing key and ensures it does not update to the MRU position.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a non-existing key and ensures it returns null.

test_cases.name: testGetWithEmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an empty map and ensures it returns null.

test_cases.name: testGetWithFullMapAndUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a full map and ensures it updates to the MRU position.

test_cases.name: testGetWithFullMapWithoutUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a full map and ensures it does not update to the MRU position.
